'''奧農達加人'''('''Onondaga People<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Onondaga_people|title=Onondaga_people|3=|access-date=2015-06-30|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114002426/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Onondaga_people|dead-url=no}}</ref>''')是北美印第安人的一支，是 '''Haudenosaunee'''<ref>{{Cite book | author=[[Bruce_E._Johansen|Bruce E. Johansen]]| title = The Native peoples of North America: a history | publisher = Rutgers University Press | year = 2006 | pages = 136–138 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=yiKgBuSUPUIC&lpg=PA137&lr&as_brr=3&pg=PA136#v=onepage&q&f=false | isbn = 978-0-8135-3899-0}}</ref>的其中之一民族。，Haudenosaunee是一個因傳統、信仰及文化價值而結盟好幾百年的土著民族聯盟，又稱作'''易洛魁聯盟'''('''Iroquois'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iroquois|title=Iroquois|3=|access-date=2015-08-24|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220125123/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iroquois|dead-url=no}}</ref>)。Haudenosaunee共有六個民族，包含了[[莫霍克人|莫霍克人]](Mohawk<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mohawk_people|title=Mohawk_people|3=|access-date=2015-08-28|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110222706/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mohawk_people|dead-url=no}}</ref>)、[[奧奈達人|奧奈達人]](Oneida<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oneida_people|title=Oneida_people|3=|access-date=2015-08-28|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224132226/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oneida_people|dead-url=no}}</ref>)、[[卡尤加人|卡尤加人]](Cayuga<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cayuga_people|title=Cayuga_people|3=|access-date=2015-08-28|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127012316/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cayuga_people|dead-url=no}}</ref>)、[[塞內卡人|塞內卡人]](Seneca<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seneca_people|title=Seneca_people|3=|access-date=2015-08-28|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125031215/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seneca_people|dead-url=no}}</ref>)、奧農達加人(Onondaga)和[[塔斯卡洛拉人|塔斯卡洛拉人]](Tuscarora<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuscarora_people|title=Tuscarora_people|3=|access-date=2015-08-28|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123230102/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuscarora_people|dead-url=no}}</ref>)民族。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.onondaganation.org/aboutus/|title=http://www.onondaganation.org/about us|3=|access-date=2015-08-24|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129013322/https://www.onondaganation.org/aboutus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''Haudenosaunee'''是他們對自己的稱呼，意思是“住在長屋的人們”，也可以譯為"長屋民族"，因為長屋生活是他們共同都有的文化特色，而外界普遍都以'''易洛魁聯盟'''稱呼他們，意譯為“和平與力量之聯盟”。<ref name="timeline1">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/?id=zibNDBchPkMC&lpg=PP1&dq=encyclopedia%20haudenosaunee&pg=PA135# v=onepage&q=|title=Encyclopedia of the Haudenosaunee pg.135 |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|accessdate=2010-04-02|isbn=978-0-313-30880-2|year=2000}}</ref> 。

原先的易洛魁聯盟往往被稱作「五族同盟」，由五大部族莫霍克人、奧奈達人、奧農達加人、塞內卡人和卡尤加人組成。 1772年，塔斯卡洛拉人加入，因此聯盟成為「六族同盟」。

